title: NFL - Which University Has Produced the Most Active NFL Players?, USA, Unknown
name: NFL - Which University Has Produced the Most Active NFL Players?, USA, Unknown
description: There is a three way tie among Florida, Georgia, and Miami for active NFL players. Each can claim 48 players as alumni of their respective schools.This dataset was compiled using the 2007-2008 rosters found online at www.nfl.com. Accessed on 9.5.07.Schools were geocoded using their latitude and longitude coordinates.
